{{ComponentStats:sc.fiji:Helmholtz_Analysis}}This plugin allows to analyze local direction and frequency of sinusoidal waves. The output are optionally smoothed ''lambda'' (inversely proportional to the frequency) and ''phi'' (direction in degrees).

See also http://www.optinav.info/Helmholtz_Analysis.htm

